.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-10::.
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, lettuce
There are 2 different nationalities: turkish, dutch
The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, software-developer
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, snowmobile
1. the person eating cabbage is not to the left of the dutch##8
2. the person driving the car is the person driving the car##1
3. the person eating lettuce is somewhere to the right of the doctor##5
4. the person driving the car is not to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##8
5. the person driving the snowmobile is not to the left of the person eating lettuce##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |         2          |
| Food        | cabbage | lettuce            |
| Nationality       | dutch | turkish              |
| Job         | doctor  | software-developer |
| Transport   | car     | snowmobile         |

