.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-20::.
There 2 different types of food: corn, plum
The people have 2 different jobs:  entrepreneur, nurse
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, april
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, scooter
1. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the right of the person eating plum##8
2. the nurse is on the right of the person eating plum##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |
| Food          | plum         | corn    |
| Job           | entrepreneur | nurse   |
| Birthday   | october   | april    |
| Transport     | boat         | scooter |

 